  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b014b7d0-53f4-43d1-8ff1-96f4e1c2ad16\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3a97047d-02e8-4106-896f-0f4fb74184c2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-408bd70e-99ed-4028-8cac-4ff697d5922e\"><a href=\"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\" class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-408bd70e-99ed-4028-8cac-4ff697d5922e\", \"link\": \"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\"}' target=\"_blank\">https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-deccf8df-2770-429b-ad7d-ef395fb9aad0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail __se_link\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"oglink\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-deccf8df-2770-429b-ad7d-ef395fb9aad0\", \"link\": \"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fimgnews.pstatic.net%2Fimage%2F296%2F2025%2F02%2F02%2F0000086326_001_20250202182112490.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw800%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\" class=\"se-oglink-info __se_link\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"oglink\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-deccf8df-2770-429b-ad7d-ef395fb9aad0\", \"link\": \"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\"}'>\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">&quot;한약이 간 손상&quot;속설…그건 오해였다고?</strong>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">일부 의사는 아직도 &#x27;한약 유해론&#x27;을 들먹인다. 한약이 많이 불법 유통됐던 시절엔 그럴 위험이 실제로 높았다. 일부 의사들의 이런 시각이 &quot;한약을 잘못 먹었다간 간이 나빠진다&quot;는 속설의 일부 원인이 된 것으로 추정된</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">n.news.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-deccf8df-2770-429b-ad7d-ef395fb9aad0\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://n.news.naver.com/article/296/0000086326?cds&#x3D;news_edit\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fimgnews.pstatic.net%2Fimage%2F296%2F2025%2F02%2F02%2F0000086326_001_20250202182112490.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw800%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\"}}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4831f08e-9d4f-4152-ae6a-ffefdbe87549\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2446f9f8-1256-4b1a-8d4a-816fc1ae5fca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-45f6b477-861a-402c-ab84-8d46860dbdd6\"> 드디어 한약 복용과 간 기능 사이의 오해를 해소할 수 있는 연구 결과가 나왔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-174a2740-09cf-4c40-8e57-8b960e6dd351\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-13831ab0-17fa-402e-9739-97adf6503b33\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2922f7e9-ca08-4040-9335-b0e1ce250af0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-47e5343b-fa1a-4e70-bdd0-53a9e2fde66e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3ff74e3a-4f1b-4d51-8a09-4f31b4b625c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b734cf82-3994-4f4c-b930-cddbc2f4ad00\">내용을 요약하면,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ea2f7411-76fd-4ce5-a232-c5565f224a47\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a9d02a34-b77b-4eb6-af74-75bafca4e91d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-21f25463-00c3-448a-a8a1-dd1d3e8cd44e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-21f25463-00c3-448a-a8a1-dd1d3e8cd44e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4d0b8e3d65e77c73.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"720\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1023\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4d0b8e3d65e77c73.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4d0b8e3d65e77c73.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"710\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f7c44c0-e917-426a-bdce-21aa1914a86f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-344310d0-a740-4fe7-bf55-0a1403bbd669\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-258470a7-3edb-4064-a4f2-add236be6c9c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c4971c5c-ab61-48be-af6e-5549ab675fd4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-443091c3-31ad-4137-ad7b-0d50a53e2ce7\">건강한 사람이 한약을 먹고 간이 나빠질 확률은 매우 낮다는 연구 결과가 나왔다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0c160385-9af5-4f49-b80b-11b1f1743b30\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-84212f27-9697-450b-b549-2ad4eea496e7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-75e30fc9-e73a-47a6-b4b2-5e5e9afab419\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-320b2367-6303-4e1c-a983-42ab8136016c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c10f77e2-07ce-4fc8-93c0-244d802ab042\">연구팀은 &#x27;약물 유발성 간손상(DILI)&#x27; 진단을 받은 환자 </span><span style=\"color:#ff0010;\" class=\"se-fs-fs30 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9d1d887d-39ce-4244-a8f9-0dcdda213a02\">67만여명</span><span style=\"color:#ff0010;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9808ba0e-3e8a-40d3-b28b-245d4e22f510\">​</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dcc04620-bca1-4c75-9c11-5685bab2d120\">을 조사∙분석한 결과 이같이 나타났다고 밝혔다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-27ecf00d-8fc5-418d-8e28-751fcec88eab\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d918899-0c67-4208-8808-fe886dca6431\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc8aa545-a7c7-4b5d-907a-9438ca4f0929\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f8a19f61-15f3-4565-896d-5339e10ccd22\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e7d0f4a5-b7a5-4388-90cc-ce471d3f3e77\">연구 결과에 따르면 참가자가 양방 병의원을 방문하거나 의약품을 처방받은 뒤 3~15일 사이에 &#x27;약물 유발성 간 손상&#x27;을 일으킬 확률이 상대적으로 더 높은 것으로 나타났다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9e5aeff-395c-413f-90ba-f17c25f2f88d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1b3eab56-1de5-422f-9b0b-a96e15d46a32\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5f7319d-7e99-4d08-8237-20a3427b47a3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b5f7319d-7e99-4d08-8237-20a3427b47a3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54987cd9ac0afde6.jpg", \"originalWidth\" : \"2480\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3507\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54987cd9ac0afde6.jpg" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/54987cd9ac0afde6.jpg" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1590b6e0-66bd-4e66-a53b-c18cac979393\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-73b17204-2759-4a5a-968a-647fd5786d0a\"><span style=\"color:#ff0010;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cdde402d-482e-4055-ae0a-052c445db6fa\">양방 병의원에서 약</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f1d6348-ae8f-4d3b-a134-bd8c7fe6f9c6\">을 처방받은 사람</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-38a239ae-42b3-4f27-bbee-0782941fa7a0\">은 그렇지 않은 사람에 비해 DILI를 일으킬 </span><span style=\"color:#ff0010;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0ab51ad8-7b91-47cd-add8-007c3cf61dce\"><u>위험이 144% </u></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8096abf8-beb6-4508-8774-e2c453c4b84b\">높아져</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-50ed3e52-9929-4480-8a24-c0d004ee9e06\"> 통계적으로 유의했다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b3a0a8d3-5f43-402c-8f7b-f006b0064fd5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27c561e9-51e9-474d-ba78-f6d27619f5a5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ee70c0f-baf2-4e95-9b1d-421e5fedb973\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9ee70c0f-baf2-4e95-9b1d-421e5fedb973\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dc999f4f1774a35d.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2480\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3507\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dc999f4f1774a35d.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dc999f4f1774a35d.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f04c19a7-f782-4557-8a13-63891ec0828d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a6a9ff8-2952-4ba0-836f-7ba2455025fb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-38ea5ac2-599b-4e3c-8767-04020b8bc87c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-155eb7c4-969b-4519-8123-40f594099000\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-adeaf145-e9be-4df2-90c2-b44224c0a534\">한방 병의원을 방문한 사람은 그렇지 않은 사람에 비해 DILI를 일으킬 </span><span style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs30 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ef23ea37-c8ae-45ab-b2b0-588754366380\"><u>위험이 1% 이내</u></span><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ce0326d6-950c-4c58-ad90-c5cfc4274c83\">로 통계적으로 유의하지 않았고, 한방 병의원에서 한약을 처방받은 사람은 그렇지 않은 사람에 비해 DILI를 일으킬 위험 역시 유의하지 않은 것으로 나타났다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87d41d4f-68cf-488b-803b-cfc1ec737baa\"><span style=\"color:#303038;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3012342a-1697-4611-af47-548b9cb8c045\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-95e6a3c2-ccac-4123-ba72-3d8edc8cf406\"><span style=\"color:#303038;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3f1a40a8-91f8-4cae-ae63-2a6a863e2f50\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fdfd50ca-a84a-4d3c-82c1-b0d9078b687b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fdfd50ca-a84a-4d3c-82c1-b0d9078b687b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9d1928e2dc2beae3.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2480\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3508\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9d1928e2dc2beae3.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9d1928e2dc2beae3.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51448cbf-43c2-4533-bcd2-6c31eec75de7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9301a95a-81d0-410f-a989-2893185a7a39\"><span style=\"color:#303038;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-7cde2e7d-0f89-432f-ad3f-656d8994391f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-69c0f9de-485e-4399-8507-8910ba2c50e0\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-30db87f3-1aef-4f09-ae37-a9b0830f2ab8\">이수한의원에서는 한약 복용 후에도 간기능이 문제 없다는걸 환자분들께 보여드리기 위해 간수치 및 신장수치를 검사할 수 있는 혈액검사기도 도입해서 활용하고 있었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ceb2ed4c-afb3-413b-820c-65b8545d8ee7\"><span style=\"color:#303038;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1838f71e-82fc-45cb-834f-1c7f515b5dfb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59edc666-ffca-4346-9aaa-3f691a7551fa\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5ff40a28-1a55-47e0-817b-d4262733dbf6\">이번 연구로 한약 먹으면 혹시나 간 기능 나빠져서 간 수치 올라갈까 걱정된다는 오해가 완전히 해소되길 기대해 봅니다.  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
